        <body>
            <pb n="1R"/>
            <p rend="align(right)"><placeName>Baltimore</placeName>
                <date>13. Decr. 1836</date>.</p>
            <p>Dear <addressee>Isaac</addressee>.</p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">I am now closing the castor oil business<lb/> for this year and am
                desirous of settling all accts. connected<lb/> with it. You must do me the favor to
                call upon <persName>Doctr.<lb/> Dyott</persName> and request him to pay you the bal.
                of $16.14<lb/>100.<lb/> farther orders for bottles will come into next year's
                business.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)"> Request <persName>Mr. Sol: Levy</persName> to close the oil in his
                hands at<lb/> One dollar if he cannot do better.</p>
            <p rend="indent(8)">Yrs,</p>
            <p rend="indent(8)">
                <persName role="author">D. Judah</persName>
            </p>
            <p>Dear <addressee>Isaac</addressee></p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">I received your letter for per <add>שבת</add><add>?</add>, I was not
                at home<lb/> when he Brought yours he did not leave word where he stayed Else I
                should<lb/> have been glad to talk on him and invite him to my house <persName>Mr
                    Jacobs</persName><lb/> the <add>?</add> is gone to
                    <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName> he is <add>?</add> not much to Depend on
                what<lb/> he says he told us he received 200 Dollars of <persName>Mr
                    Etting</persName> but <persName>Mr Etting</persName><lb/> told us last
                    <add>Hebrew</add> he only paid him for himself and some $60— so you<lb/> must
                not believe what he says we receivd. a letter from
                    <persName>man<add>?</add></persName> last<lb/> week she is well give my respect
                to <persName>Mr &amp; Mrs Peixotto</persName> and the young<lb/> ladies and the
                young gentleman and the same from your Aunt no news<lb/> I remain your friend
                    /<persName role="author">Zalma Rehine</persName></p>
            <p>I have not seen <persName>Mr Cohen</persName> yet so let that stand as it is at present<lb/>
                <add>?</add>stood that your book is liked in <placeName>Jamaica</placeName>.</p>
            <pb n="2V"/>
            <p rend="indent(5)"><addressee>Mr. Isaac Leezer</addressee>.</p>
            <p rend="indent(7)">
                <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(4)"><add>?</add>: <persName>Henry</persName></p>
        </body>
